query:
SELECT id AS id,
       plan_id AS plan_id,
       jurisdiction_id AS jurisdiction_id,
       jurisdiction_parent_id AS jurisdiction_parent_id,
       jurisdiction_name AS jurisdiction_name,
       jurisdiction_depth AS jurisdiction_depth,
       jurisdiction_path AS jurisdiction_path,
       jurisdiction_name_path AS jurisdiction_name_path,
       is_virtual_jurisdiction AS is_virtual_jurisdiction,
       totstruct AS totstruct,
       rooms_eligible AS rooms_eligible,
       rooms_sprayed AS rooms_sprayed,
       sprayed_rooms_eligible AS sprayed_rooms_eligible,
       sprayed_rooms_sprayed AS sprayed_rooms_sprayed,
       foundstruct AS foundstruct,
       notsprayed AS notsprayed,
       noteligible AS noteligible,
       sprayedstruct AS sprayedstruct,
       totareas AS totareas,
       targareas AS targareas,
       visitedareas AS visitedareas,
       targstruct AS targstruct,
       perctvisareaseffect AS perctvisareaseffect,
       spraycovtarg AS spraycovtarg,
       foundcoverage AS foundcoverage,
       spraysuccess AS spraysuccess,
       roomcov AS roomcov,
       num_health_centers_below_90_se AS num_health_centers_below_90_se,
       num_spray_areas_below_90_se AS num_spray_areas_below_90_se,
       structures_remaining_to_90_se AS structures_remaining_to_90_se,
       tla_days_to_90_se AS tla_days_to_90_se
FROM public.zambia_irs_jurisdictions
WHERE plan_id = '7e4aba56-d5cc-5b3c-9e01-966e757c389e'
ORDER BY jurisdiction_depth ASC,
         jurisdiction_name ASC
LIMIT 15000;
